_header: Over all I find they [tho] be sorry
Subjects: human life; transitoriness, of life; evils of the time
_description: An English couplet in a Latin tract De relinquendis temporalibus bonis

BodAsh1280.Transcription:
over al ich finde tho be soriouer al ich finde mi lef
                    blodi
